WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: uKM2kZG3Z_Y

NOTE Language: en

00:00:06.073 --> 00:00:09.960
So this is very important today to do Vishnumaya’s thing

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:16.232
and I am sure now very happy with the tour of America.

00:00:16.312 --> 00:00:23.060
This time I’m really happy because I think it
has worked in most of the places very well,

00:00:23.140 --> 00:00:28.574
and if it has not worked, one should
not feel guilty, but face the problem,

00:00:28.654 --> 00:00:36.884
why it has not worked and the problem
lies with Sahaja Yogis and nobody else.

00:00:36.964 --> 00:00:40.575
You shouldn’t blame anybody else for it.

00:00:40.655 --> 00:00:43.901
Just see yourself, what mistakes you must have committed.

00:00:43.981 --> 00:00:48.732
Could be a small or big mistake. Whatever it is, face it.

00:00:48.812 --> 00:00:52.541
There’s no harm in saying, “I have done mistake.”

00:00:52.621 --> 00:01:00.597
But if you say, “Sorry,” means it goes there,
straight off. No, “I have committed a mistake.”

00:01:00.677 --> 00:01:08.887
To admit that is very gracious, very beautiful
and very kind to yourself for your benevolence.

00:01:08.967 --> 00:01:15.044
In Sahaja Yoga it’s one of the biggest
mantras for all the Western people.

00:01:15.124 --> 00:01:23.185
They should all the time say to all the
trees, all the nature around, “I am not guilty”.

00:01:23.265 --> 00:01:28.146
Your ecological problem will improve

00:01:28.226 --> 00:01:32.182
because then you won’t do
wrong things to spoil your ecology.

00:01:32.262 --> 00:01:35.082
You’ll be careful because
you spoil it and you’ll feel guilty,

00:01:35.162 --> 00:01:38.234
“Oh, I should not have done this. Oh, I should not.”

00:01:38.314 --> 00:01:41.275
But why did you do in the first place is the point.

00:01:41.355 --> 00:01:44.635
So now, next time you are not going to do it.

00:01:44.715 --> 00:01:51.788
So many of our problems will be solved
if you face them and correct them boldly.

00:01:51.868 --> 00:01:57.885
It’s possible for Sahaja Yogis because you are
separated from your being, you’re away from it.

00:01:57.965 --> 00:02:02.493
You can see your body, you can
see your mind, you can see your ego,

00:02:02.573 --> 00:02:07.381
you can see all of those things
and you know how to put them right.

00:02:07.461 --> 00:02:11.288
You are not that, you know, so you are the spirit

00:02:11.368 --> 00:02:16.816
and with the light of the spirit
you can correct all these things.

00:02:16.896 --> 00:02:21.688
But this guilt is something where it
stops you completely from correcting

00:02:21.768 --> 00:02:31.099
or doing anything better about it or bringing
any constructive thing to your own mind.

00:02:31.179 --> 00:02:38.310
This will solve many problems for
America, as well as for all the Western world.

00:02:38.390 --> 00:02:43.362
Same with the Indians, that they should
not think that if they are generous a little bit

00:02:43.442 --> 00:02:47.829
they can get rid of their
mistakes. See, they have to face it.

00:02:47.909 --> 00:02:54.396
It’s a different style. Indians are very clever, you
know, they know how to find excuses and escapes.

00:02:54.476 --> 00:02:58.594
But after all, it is Vishnumaya.

00:02:58.674 --> 00:03:03.529
She will show you that there is no escape, just face it.

00:03:03.609 --> 00:03:11.316
There’s no need to condemn yourself, no need
to, in any way, degrade yourself or to feel inferior,

00:03:11.396 --> 00:03:15.404
but to be superior as the spirit, I see.

00:03:15.484 --> 00:03:19.719
Like I would say, “All right, Nirmala,
I see you very well now, you did this.”

00:03:19.799 --> 00:03:21.992
Separate yourself from yourself.

00:03:22.072 --> 00:03:26.967
You can talk on the mirror. You
can go to the river and talk there

00:03:27.047 --> 00:03:30.122
or you can go to an ocean and tell them that,

00:03:30.202 --> 00:03:34.807
“See, I’ve done this mistake
and now I’m not going to do it.”

00:03:34.887 --> 00:03:37.377
You can make promises to all of these elements.

00:03:37.457 --> 00:03:43.023
Once you make these promises, this
Vishnumaya will receive the message

00:03:43.103 --> 00:03:46.925
and She won’t enter into any one
of these elements to disturb you.
